Module com.example.cs213_cafe_project
Package com.example.cs213_cafe_project.data

Class Order

java.lang.Object
com.example.cs213_cafe_project.data.Order
public class Order extends Object
Implementation for orders in our project. Each order object consists of an integer order number and a hashmap structure for the order itself. Keys: menuItems, Values: quantity of corresponding menuItem
